"title": "8131: guidance, results of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8131",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Wise counsel, advice and direction from God or his servants, if carefully followed, will enrich and benefit those to whom it is given.</p>\n<h2>Guidance resulting in military victory</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:17-2Sam5:20\">2SA 5:17–5:20</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:8-1Chr14:11\">1CH 14:8–14:11</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh6:1-Josh6:21\">JOS 6:1–6:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh8:1-Josh8:22\">JOS 8:1–8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:33-Judg7:25\">JDG 6:33–7:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam5:22-2Sam5:25\">2SA 5:22–5:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr14:13-1Chr14:16\">1CH 14:13–14:16</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance resulting in safety</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:1-Matt2:23\">MAT 2:1–2:23</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Guidance resulting in personal benefit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:1-2Sam2:4\">2SA 2:1–2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:10-Gen24:27\">GEN 24:10–24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:1-Gen41:49\">GEN 41:1–41:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs5:1-2Kgs5:14\">2KI 5:1–5:14</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance resulting in the appointment of leaders</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:1-Acts13:3\">ACT 13:1–13:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:15-1Kgs19:21\">1KI 19:15–19:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:12-Luke6:16\">LUK 6:12–6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:15-Acts1:26\">ACT 1:15–1:26</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance inspiring confidence</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:11\">ACT 23:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen46:1-Gen46:7\">GEN 46:1–46:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:11\">ACT 18:9–18:11</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance resulting in spiritual growth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:9\">PRO 9:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod16:1-Exod16:30\">EXO 16:1–16:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:3-1Kgs19:18\">1KI 19:3–19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:1-Acts9:19\">ACT 9:1–9:19</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance eliciting praise and worship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:19-Dan2:23\">DAN 2:19–2:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:15-Exod15:21\">EXO 14:15–15:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:1-2Sam7:29\">2SA 7:1–7:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:23-Ps73:28\">PSA 73:23–73:28</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance leading to obedience</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:1-Gen12:5\">GEN 12:1–12:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:9-Gen6:22\">GEN 6:9–6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:11-Judg6:27\">JDG 6:11–6:27</a></p>\n<h2>Guidance disregarded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:16-Matt19:22\">MAT 19:16–19:22</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:22\">MRK 10:17–10:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:23\">LUK 18:18–18:23</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:1-Gen3:6\">GEN 3:1–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:1-1Kgs22:38\">1KI 22:1–22:38</a></p>",
